warning.warningAndCautionPara: Aircraft characteristic in one engine inoperative during takeoff roll, generate sudden yaw to inoperative engine.

Abort takeoff using step wise power idle (from MAX POWER, reduce to mid range, then smoothly to IDLE) is recommended. There will be a lot of directional changes, control the aircraft direction using rudder cautiously.
